554
00:33:09,000 --> 00:33:10,799
Color and such are just superficial things.

555
00:33:11,160 --> 00:33:13,119
Can't white or pink ones become black?

556
00:33:14,240 --> 00:33:15,920
Yes, absolutely they can.

557
00:33:19,359 --> 00:33:21,440
Girl, what number is this?

558
00:33:23,960 --> 00:33:24,599
Two...

559
00:33:25,319 --> 00:33:26,240
hundred and fifty.

560
00:33:29,240 --> 00:33:31,559
What a pity, truly a pity.

