563
00:33:35,119 --> 00:33:36,039
Come quickly and greet the young lady.

564
00:33:39,000 --> 00:33:40,359
I was just talking about this girl.

565
00:33:47,000 --> 00:33:48,559
So the role Director Ling cameoed as

566
00:33:48,559 --> 00:33:49,720
