579
00:34:31,800 --> 00:34:32,440
Little Black.

580
00:34:35,239 --> 00:34:36,679
Simpleton, you be careful.

581
00:34:36,880 --> 00:34:37,960
Little Black bites people.

582
00:34:41,920 --> 00:34:42,639
Little Black.

583
00:34:46,960 --> 00:34:47,639
Little Black.

584
00:34:49,960 --> 00:34:50,679
Little Black.

585
00:34:54,960 --> 00:34:57,400
Little Black, my treasure.

586
00:35:00,960 --> 00:35:03,360
That domineering, vicious, selfish

587
00:35:03,360 --> 00:35:04,920
and utterly inhuman Fifth Princess in the palace

588
00:35:05,400 --> 00:35:06,639
actually dares to covet you.

589
00:35:07,519 --> 00:35:09,159
How could this young lady let her have her way?

590
00:35:10,599 --> 00:35:11,079
Simpleton.

591
00:35:11,679 --> 00:35:13,039
Go and fetch the pastries, quickly!

592
00:35:20,440 --> 00:35:21,199
