593
00:35:21,679 --> 00:35:23,519
That domineering, vicious, selfish

594
00:35:23,519 --> 00:35:26,320
and utterly heartless Fifth Princess is none other than me.

595
00:35:26,960 --> 00:35:29,320
She came to your mansion to steal a pig.

596
00:35:36,480 --> 00:35:37,519
Blackie, be good.

597
00:35:37,639 --> 00:35:38,679
Here, have a bite.

598
00:35:41,079 --> 00:35:42,320
