599
00:35:44,960 --> 00:35:46,639
I should still ask my brother to fetch a doctor.

600
00:35:49,360 --> 00:35:51,159
You fool, watch Little Black carefully.

601
00:36:01,159 --> 00:36:01,760
What is it?

602
00:36:06,480 --> 00:36:07,159
You fed him?

603
00:36:10,679 --> 00:36:12,719
It seems Little Black quite likes you.

604
00:36:14,719 --> 00:36:16,199
From now on, you are responsible for taking care of Little Black.

605
00:36:17,239 --> 00:36:19,400
If you dare let him lose a single hair,

606
00:36:20,159 --> 00:36:21,920
you won't eat for a day.

607
00:36:45,199 --> 00:36:45,800
Young Master Xiu.

608
00:36:47,199 --> 00:36:47,760
Young Master Xiu!

609
00:36:47,880 --> 00:36:48,320
