616
00:37:14,800 --> 00:37:17,800
Seventh Cousin, you won't find A Lan.

617
00:37:38,519 --> 00:37:39,159
Why?

618
00:37:40,119 --> 00:37:43,320
A pig thief has come to the Meng Mansion.

619
00:38:11,519 --> 00:38:14,039
Just like that domineering Fifth Princess,

620
00:38:14,679 --> 00:38:16,639
coveting our Meng Mansion's little black pig.
